NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
H.I., Defendant,
and
M.D., Defendant-Petitioner. In the Matter of the Guardianship of M.D., a Minor-Respondent. C-839 September Term 2017
080286 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-396/397-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
